. I was able to successfully modify the derived_boxes.py in the EasyGUI module to get the desired result.

Where the boolbox function is defined I changed

    if reply == choices[0]:
        return True
    else:
        return False


TO:

    if reply == choices[0]:
        return True
    elif reply == choices[1]:
        return False
    else:
        return None

