The problem is:
      auto A_ = Z3_mk_interpolant(ctx, A);
and how it is used.

You have to take a reference to A_. From C++ you can do it by wrapping the call in an expression construct.

      auto A_ = expr(ctx, Z3_mk_interpolant(ctx, A));

